{"tid":117942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行人專區點洋燭求婚鬧劇收場","createTime":"2017-02-12T15:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T23:34:50.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5ea2a601cd3dfdd72f4e334bc31a574aae61063","tid":117942,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"在港鐵縱火事件陰霾下，旺角今晚(12日)上演的一場求婚記，惟因途人擔心有火警危險，結果以鬧劇收場。晚上8時許，21歲的Amy在西洋菜南街行人專用區，打算燃點放在地上、砌成心形的數十支紅色洋燭，再單膝跪地向較她年長30年的男友求婚。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，Amy點火的行徑立即惹來途人擔心，恐變縱火危及公眾安全，有街坊隨即致電報警，數名消防員及警員接報到場，阻止她燃點洋燭。Amy最後只好在欠缺燭光下，向男友求婚，幸最終成功。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從事自由工作的Amy指，因與男友年齡差距大，兩人拍拖一年多以來，父母及朋友都反對，她冀今次公開求婚表明決心，表達愛情無年齡界限的信念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170212/mobile/bkn-20170212210639385-0212_00822_001.html#popupGallery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170212%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170212210639385-0212_00822_001.html%23popupGallery&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f0373c17\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170212/mobile/bkn-20170212210639385-0212_00822_001.html#popupGallery</a><br />\n<br />\n又買廣告？"},{"pid":"0531a74893e4bec2fd386d19ee60e1dd163479b7","tid":117942,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:37:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4dc50242f31bdec5e343ece75dfa2dec22723fe","tid":117942,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:38:13.000Z","msg":"21歲女向個50歲呀叔跪地求婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5166a7ceb7d6c7136b02e815d05c1907827c7e1a","tid":117942,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:44:58.000Z","msg":"條女個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 